Name: Brave Doggy Quest
About the game: Mysterious creatures have stolen your entire supply of your favorite bones and scattered them all over the place, but they never imagined that they had contacted the wrong dog! In this 2D platformer, to satisfy your hunger and thirst for revenge, you embark on a long journey to take loot from your enemies, who have hidden among deadly traps and dangerous obstacles. Can you overcome all the incredible levels and get to the very end? You play as Athena the Dog, overcome mysterious creatures using your dexterity and abilities Peculiarities: - Nice graphics - Nice soundtrack by ChillMindscapes - an unforgettable adventure
